name: DISTRO - Tapes
description: Tapes of various genres we've received from other labels through trades. Click on title for samples. Buy multiple products to save on shipping! Solothus | Ritual of the Horned Skull (Nihilistic Holocaust) Old-school Death/Doom from Finland. Really great stuff! Storm of Darkness | The Legions of Xue (The Northern Cold Productions) Pure Black Metal from Colombia! The Transmutations | The Hundred Years (Preposterous Creations) Amazing British Neofolk.
